{{> header}}

<h2>Event Registration Confirmation</h2>
<p>Dear {{user.firstName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for registering for <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>. We're excited to have you join us!</p>

<h3>Event Details:</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{dateFormat eventDate "MMMM D, YYYY"}}</li>
    <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{dateFormat eventDate "h:mm A"}}</li>
    <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{eventLocation}}</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

<p>We look forward to seeing you at the event!</p>

{{> footer}}